sics and 'The Illusion of Understanding']]Jul 8, 2012%0a%3c * [[#&lpos=RR Voices]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/steve-clemons/ |  http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/front/images/authors/45x42/steveClemons.jpg ]] [[http://www.theatlantic.com/steve-clemons/ | Steve Clemons]]!!! [[#&lpos=RR Voices]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2012/07/air-force-drones-trail-civilian-auto-traffic-in-new-mexico/259517/ | Air Force Drones Trail Civilian Auto Traffic in&hellip;]]Jul 6, 2012%0a%3c * [[#&lpos=RR Voices]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/clive-crook/ |  http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/front/images/authors/45x42/cliveCrook.jpg ]] [[http://www.theatlantic.com/clive-crook/ | Clive Crook]]!!! [[#&lpos=RR Voices]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2012/07/health-care-and-the-court-who-won/259431/ | Health Care and the Court: Who Won?]]Jul 4, 2012%0a%3c %0a%3c !! [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/voices/#correspondents | Correspondents]]%0a%3c %0a%3c * [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/jack-balkin | Jack M. Balkin]]!!! [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/national/archive/2012/06/the-court-affirms-our-social-contract/259186/ | The Court Affirms Our Social Contract]]%0a%3c * [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/andrew-cohen | Andrew Cohen]]!!! [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/business/archive/2012/06/having-it-all-how-about-doing-the-best-i-can/258898/ | 'Having It All'? How About: 'Doing The Best I Can'?]]%0a%3c * [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/wendy-kaminer | Wendy Kaminer]]!!! [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com/national/archive/2012/06/juvenile-sentencing-alitos-misguided-dissent/259007/ | Juvenile Sentencing: Alito's Misguided Dissent]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#&lpos=RR Correspondents]][[http://www.theatlantic.com:80/voices/#correspondents |  View All Correspondents ]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ||%0a%3c ||[[http://www.th